Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:34.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:36.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:40.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼啊 是情書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:43.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是 這是普通的信而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:44.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大家現在不都這樣玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:45.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.35,0:00:47.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:48.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:51.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,待會我也給由加莉寫一封
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.32,0:00:52.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的好意我心領了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:55.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但上課的時候要認真聽課啊 美奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:57.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比起學習 還是友情比較重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:01.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最近女生之間流行寫信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:02.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好像是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:05.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說不定也有在寫情書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:09.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她們寫什麼都很認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:10.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:12.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,情書嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.21,0:01:15.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,直接用嘴說就好了 居然還特意寫在紙上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:17.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她們還真不嫌麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:19.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看來她們挺閒的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:28.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}對不起對不起對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:30.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 早苗 你幹得太過了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:32.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一下就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:35.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還是要踢一腳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:38.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,開始上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:42.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,翻到課本76頁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:50.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學也在寫信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:55.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說到底高木同學也只是個普通的女生而已嘛
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:45.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:58.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是信 誰送來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:00.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼要寫給我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:03.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說不定也有在寫情書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:06.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不不不 這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:07.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定是誰的惡作劇…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:13.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這說不定是高木同學的惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 肯定是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:21.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 要是弄錯了該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要不是高木同學寫的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一旦我收到信件的事情暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:27.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定又會被高木同學捉弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天天氣不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是不是在瞞著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:49.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但感覺你好可疑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,臉還那麼紅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:53.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是你的錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:55.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是錯覺就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你為什麼不翻開課本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:00.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個嘛…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:03.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這和你臉紅有關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:05.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒有 我的臉也沒有紅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:08.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:10.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都說了什麼事也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:15.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是我的錯覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:20.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還有 夾在書裡的那封信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是我放的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:27.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,果然是她幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:33.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這種把戲 我完全看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:35.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:39.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我只是裝不知道而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:42.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不看看裡面寫了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:44.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 裡面寫了東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:46.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:51.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,反正又是捉弄我的內容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:56.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你幹嘛不說話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:06:00.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那既然你寫了 我就看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:02.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你現在看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:05.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:08.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為這節課下課之後就放學了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,想你在那之前答覆我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,答 答覆？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:19.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,需要作出回復的信件 也就是說裡面有提問
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:22.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,內容難道不只是惡作劇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說不定也有在寫情書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:28.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也就是說有可能是情書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:30.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:37.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道是情書什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又默不出聲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我看 我會看的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:48.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看了就行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:53.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,照那麼說 裡面寫的肯定是惡作劇之類的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:56.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那無論裡面寫了什麼 我都要保持鎮定不被她捉弄到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:58.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,堂堂正正地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:01.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:02.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:06.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然肯定是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:09.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但要真是情書的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:13.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我該…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:23.13,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\frx8\fry0\frz352.3\move(641.6,408,643.2,308.8,195,4908)}給西片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:23.13,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\frz345.8\frx2\fry4\move(657.6,917.2,660.8,840.4,195,4908)\fad(200,0)}今天一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,直接跟我說不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:38.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,現在流行寫信嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:45.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且 我也想看看你會有怎樣的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:49.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你果然是在捉弄我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:50.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,吵死了 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:09.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,入學典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:20.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 麻煩你專門跑一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼 我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:24.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:28.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,新生 你的名字叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:30.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,您問我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我叫西片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:36.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 祝賀你入學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:45.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在接下來的一年裡 你們就是一起學習的伙伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:48.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不會要求你們每時每刻都保持融洽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:52.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但希望你們儘可能和諧相處
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是掉到哪裡去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:59.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嘛 剛開學也沒有什麼需要嘮叨的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,突然就來了個睡過頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:05.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:08.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的膽量我倒是挺佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:09.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:10.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:13.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我叫西片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:16.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算了 坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:18.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:26.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好顯眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:28.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在被定性為遲到型角色之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:31.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,得趕緊和大家打好交道 解開誤會才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:37.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,田邊老師 能打擾一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,車子好像晚點才到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:44.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,遲到了嗎 那儀式也要推遲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:46.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:50.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,現在入學典禮的準備時間延長了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好像會耽擱不少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:54.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在這期間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:58.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我們來決定座位順序
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:07.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:10.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,偏偏抽到了最後一排最角落的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:12.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,放在平時會是件令人高興的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:14.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但對現在的我來說只有壞處
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:16.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,本來就一個人也不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:20.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,現在左邊和後面都沒有人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:22.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且旁邊坐的還是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你真的睡過頭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:29.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她向我搭話了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為老師好像跟你說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:36.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,該怎麼說好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是沒有遲到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:41.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我都明明準時到學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:45.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都怪一個叫高木同學的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 所有人去體育館
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:52.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,安靜一點 不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:54.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:59.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:02.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:08.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:15.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你們總有一天會得到選舉權這筆無價的財富
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:20.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最重要的是要選擇值得信賴的政治家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:25.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,請務必 讓爸爸和媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:30.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,演講太長了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:30.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:33.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大叔的演講就是長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,無論在小學還是中學都沒什麼變化嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過開學第一天就遲到 你也是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:42.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要吵了 回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:52.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:58.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:00.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快點坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:05.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天就到此結束了 明天開始正式上課
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:08.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要因為是開學典禮就得意忘形 要乖乖回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:17.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我來猜猜今天西片遲到的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:20.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是一次就猜中 那就算我贏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:26.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一次是猜不中的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:31.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是去送還失物了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:33.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:35.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 你太吵了西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:37.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼你會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:49.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:56.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:59.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,做自我介紹的時候你不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:09.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的反應是怎麼回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:12.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說 那一塊很吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:24.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你幫我撿回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,以後請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:34.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:37.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,換座位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:42.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,七十二 七十三
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:49.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,七十四 七十五
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有點肌肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:11.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她還沒來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:45.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:48.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你知道嗎 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:57.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天要換座位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:05.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:06.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,班會課的時候換
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:09.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,班會課不是第一節嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:24.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}高木同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:24.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:30.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:38.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為 好久沒有換過座位了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:49.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然也有值得期待的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:54.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但我還是覺得西片旁邊的位置比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:00.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她又要捉弄我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:03.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所有人都抽籤了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:24.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 按簽上面寫的調換座位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:26.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片是多少號
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:28.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,29號
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:32.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 又是在最後一排呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:33.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:37.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我在中間那列的第一位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:43.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我們離得好遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:46.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:49.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉 考試的時候告訴我答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:54.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不對 一般來說那算抄襲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是相互幫助啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:57.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈要怎麼幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:59.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我從後面給你加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喲 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:04.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你坐這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:05.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 是對面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:09.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 要是在附近就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:10.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:17.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我最近視力變差了 不知道能不能看清黑板呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:37.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,旁邊坐的原來是西片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:39.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:42.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:46.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 你這反應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:50.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼 不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:56.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只是不能和中井坐到一塊 有點失落而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:02.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,中井的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:05.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有誰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:09.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有誰能和我換換座位嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:13.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,坐著講台的正前方 我要怎麼偷吃午飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:16.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒有正當理由的話 不可以換座位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:19.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還有木村 你跟我來教員室一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:21.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,講台正前方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:29.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我覺得還是西片旁邊的位置比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,木村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:50.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我視力不太好 我們交換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:53.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不行 我已經換好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:04.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:09.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:11.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:21.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:24.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我把座位換到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:25.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:31.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我讓中井同學和木村同學以看不見黑板為由換了座位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為中井坐到了最前面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:37.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原本坐他旁邊的我就和真野換了位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:40.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為真野個子小 坐前面比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:43.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:48.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你原本打算換到我旁邊的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:55.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個 因為我看不清黑板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:58.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:05.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:07.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,開始上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,把課本拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:10.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:12.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片想跟我說什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:16.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,從早上開始 你就一直想和我說些什麼似的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:27.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個 抱歉還晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:29.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是暑假那時的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:32.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:34.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:36.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,入學典禮那天的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:37.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你還記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:40.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片才是 虧你還記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:43.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:46.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:49.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我把它洗乾淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:55.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:57.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:01.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我是指各種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:04.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比如把手帕還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:06.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又能一起坐什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:09.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個…各種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,以後也請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:13.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I do not say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:14.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:17.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}在這篇文章裡 do是一般現在時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:21.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}這時把它變成過去式的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:47.70,Takagisan-huamian-1,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fs55\pos(1107.6,324.4)}給高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:47.70,Takagisan-huamian-1,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fs55\pos(726.4,492.4)}非常感謝
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:17.40,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:21.82,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:32.17,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:40.97,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}校庭で君のことを一番に見つけて今日は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:49.27,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて話しかけようか？ ちょっと考えるの楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:52.23,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風に揺らされるカーテン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:57.61,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不意打ちに当たる日差し
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:03:01.49,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しそうな顔を笑ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:05.41,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}照れて伏せちゃうのね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:13.50,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}憂鬱なテストも吹き飛ばせるような
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:21.80,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ、二人で秘密の約束をしたいなって提案です
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:27.22,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:31.19,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:41.45,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:17.40,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}會錯意了也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:21.82,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 這樣想著卻不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:32.17,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}瀰漫在周圍的那陣幽香 想在你的身邊靜靜感受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:40.97,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在校園的庭院 第一個發現你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:49.27,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今天要和你說些什麼呢 即便是想著這些也是一種樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:52.23,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窗簾隨風起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:57.61,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不經意地投入一束陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:03:01.49,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那美麗的容顏笑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:05.41,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}羞得我抬不起頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:13.50,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風兒喧囂 似要吹散考試的憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:21.80,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}吶 我想要和你一起 立下兩人的秘密約定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:27.22,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}會錯意了也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:31.19,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 這樣想著卻不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:41.45,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}瀰漫在周圍的那陣幽香 想在你的身邊靜靜感受
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:53.41,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}My love is forever
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:59.59,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}あなたと出逢った頃のように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.59,0:22:03.34,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}季節が変わっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:10.51,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}きっと色褪せないはずだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:34.00,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}ダイアリー会える日しるしつけてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:38.79,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}なんだか不思議ね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:49.14,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}今まで以上に夢中になれるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:56.48,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}夏の恋の魔法のせいかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.94,0:22:59.44,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}My love is forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:05.61,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}あなたと出逢った頃のように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:09.20,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}いつまでもいたいね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.24,0:23:13.08,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}ときめき大事にして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:17.79,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}青く澄んだ瞳に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:21.63,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}この胸は高鳴るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:25.46,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}季節が変わっても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:32.76,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}きっと色褪せないはずだよ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:53.41,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}My love is forever
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:59.59,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}宛如你我相逢之時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.59,0:22:03.34,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}就算四季交替
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:10.51,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}也絕不會褪色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:34.00,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}在日記裡標上和你相會的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:38.79,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}總有些不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:49.14,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}沉迷其中 更甚過往
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:56.48,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}是因為夏天的戀愛魔法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.94,0:22:59.44,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}My love is forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:05.61,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}宛如你我相逢之時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:09.20,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}想和你廝守一生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.24,0:23:13.08,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}珍惜一點一滴的感動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:17.79,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}湛藍清澄的眼瞳
