Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:25.46,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}就算四季交替
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:32.76,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}也絕不會褪色
